Name: Crown Claimer
About the game: A top down shooter where you must defend your crown at all costs! Gameplay: Gameplay consists of nothing but shooting. Enemies spawn in waves and will run to you guns blazing. Play with a friend in Co-Op mode, or if you prefer, you can play by yourself in singleplayer. Features: Play with a friend in Co-Op or by yourself in Singleplayer. Multiple enemy types and multiple arenas. Full Controller Support Completely Original OST
